name: I Ching Braided Necklace  -  Large Coin, Antique Gold
description:
The focal point for the I Ching collection is the characteristic I Ching coin. Used for centuries to represent the relationship between the energy of the earth and the universe,  I Ching is a reminder that although the world is in constant movement and change, the universe is in perfect order and balance.

The I Ching philosophy is said to bring the owner of the coin good fortune, health and prosperity. As such, this latest design from La Chance continues the original La Chance philosophy in a new, elegang and rustic design.

The I Ching Braided Necklace is set with Swarovski Crystals and incorporates the classic La Chance Zodiac ball, symbolising the beliefs of the Ancient Eastern Zodiac. 

Finished in antique gold plate

name: Lucky Bracelet  -  IP Crystal Gold
description:
The original La Chance Lucky Bracelet is inspired by the Eastern Zodiac in which the 12 animals symbolise good fortune, health and prosperity.

The 12 animal beads are handcrafted in ceramic and set among Swarovski crystals in Ion Plated Gold wheels and the distinctive La Chance logo wheel.

La Chance bracelets are worn by many Australian and International celebrities including Marcia Hines, Channel 9 weather presenter Jaynie Seal, Kim Waugh, Charli Delaney, actor Zoe Naylor and champion jockeys Kathy O'Hara and Corey Brown who both had significant wins shortly after wearing this bracelet and have since gone on to have a fairy tale run.
